{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WELCOME TO LAKE FACADE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have arrived at the mysterious Lake Facade. A secluded tranquil spot, with some of the best fishing around!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or so you've been told...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enter Lake Facade and enjoy your stay or try to solve its mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/FishingGifOptimizedSmall.gif?t=1728294511\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spend your time:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Fishing \ud83c\udfa3</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Exploring the Lake \ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Talk to the locals \ud83d\udcac</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Uncover the history and secrets of the Lake \ud83d\udcdc</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Become one with the Lake \ud83d\udc19</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/ExistenceGif.gif?t=1728294511\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A retro style puzzle/adventure game about fishing, exploring and uncovering ancient horrors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Heavily inspired by H.P. Lovecraft and other Lovecraftian mythos, blending elements into both the gameplay and story (Not just a Cthulhu squid monster).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Open ended gameplay lets you choose how you want to progress with multiple endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But the end is just the beginning...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your actions leave a permanent effect on this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you sure that's what you really want?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p