mall.gif?t=1728294511\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spend your time:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Fishing \ud83c\udfa3</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Exploring the Lake \ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Talk to the locals \ud83d\udcac</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Uncover the history and secrets of the Lake \ud83d\udcdc</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Become one with the Lake \ud83d\udc19</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/ExistenceGif.gif?t=1728294511\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A retro style puzzle/adventure game about fishing, exploring and uncovering ancient horrors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Heavily inspired by H.P. Lovecraft and other Lovecraftian mythos, blending elements into both the gameplay and story (Not just a Cthulhu squid monster).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Open ended gameplay lets you choose how you want to progress with multiple endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But the end is just the beginning...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your actions leave a permanent effect on this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you sure that's what you really want?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/extras/PSLogo3D.gif?t=1728294511\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This is the full version of Lake Facade. The original was made in 10 days for the DreadXP Dredge the Depths Jam.</strong></p>","developers":["Rexoto Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887910/header.jpg?t=1728294511","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movie